txt.en: A Dumûri scout has arrived to escort you back to Iridír
A Dumûri scout has arrived to escort you back to Iridír
You have completed your mission and should talk to the Dumûri scout.
Hamper the Ordâkhai efforts in Ambarûl by defeating soldiers and destroying their provisions in Khetsok.
Girhâzi has decided it is time to go on the offensive and has ordered an assault on the Ordâkhai camp of Khetsok.
'Let us make our way back to Iridír.'
'[placeholder], it seems your work here is done, at least for now. The assault was a success! Come, I will lead you back to Iridír.'
